channel.title: Can somebody help me making a RS private server?
channel.description:
can somebody please help me making a runescape private server? I'm getting angry because I made my server, but it won't work... I hope somebody can add me on MSN so we can talk about, and hope you'ld make a runescape private server for me, for free. I hope somebody could make, because most of you know how to make it in 5 minutes. Add me on MSN please: fivescape@live.nl
Please I would be very happy if you could make one for free, and you could be an Admin if you would. And if you finished making it, could you please send me the map, where everything is putted on, so I can edit it further?
Yours, Refive

you can make one in 20 mins. Just go on server tutorials and do How To Make A Server.
then itll just take 20 mins if youre good, just to get one started.
Requesting a coder is not allowed though
